org.slieb.throwables

Class SuppressedException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • org.slieb.throwables.SuppressedException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class SuppressedException
extends RuntimeException
    This exception class wraps checked exceptions as a runtime exceptions, so we can throw them in Functional interfaces such as Function and Supplier in a consistent manner.
    See Also:
